{"id":"wars-of-the-lord-the-book-of-the","term":"Wars of the Lord, The Book of the","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 21:14\">Num. 21:14</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 21:15\">15</a>), some unknown book so called (comp. <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 14:14\">Gen. 14:14-16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 17:8\">Ex. 17:8-16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 14:40\">Num. 14:40-45</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 21:1\">21:1-3</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 21:21\">21-25</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 21:33\">33-35</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 21:31\">31</a>. The wars here recorded might be thus designated).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 21:14","Numbers 21:15","Genesis 14:14","Exodus 17:8","Numbers 14:40","Numbers 21:1","Numbers 21:21","Numbers 21:33","Numbers 21:31"]}